Package pkgMain

Class SaveGardenView

java.lang.Object
pkgMain.View
pkgMain.SaveGardenView
public class SaveGardenView
extends View
Class - SaveGardenView, this class sets up the scene for saving a garden. Displays the garden score, a box for entering a filename, and a button to save as well as suggestions for how to improve the garden.
Author:
William Cantera, Diane Vinson, Ben Testani, Jacob Kuchma, Maria Venrooy
